								disabled="disabled">${myReservationInfo.rerequest}</textarea>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bor15 p-t-18 p-b-15 p-lr-40 p-lr-15-sm">
						<div class="mtext-109 cl2 p-b-30 p-t-30"> 주의사항 </div>
